===Etymology===
Dutch, earth-pig
===Noun===
Plural: aardvarks
#''(Zoölogy):'' A  [[mammal]] of the order [[Tubulidentata]], of the genus ''Orycteropus'', somewhat resembling a [[pig]], common in some parts of Southern Africa. It [[burrows]] in the ground, and feeds entirely on [[ant]]s, which it [[catches]] with its long, [[slimy]] tongue.

===Synonyms===
Anteater, pangolin

